detail_desc: Halterneck jumpsuit in a patterned weave with a V-neck at the front and ties at the back of the neck. Seam and detachable tie belt at the waist, side pockets, a concealed zip in one side and wide legs. Lined at the top.
5-pocket jeans in washed, stretch denim with hard-worn details in a looser fit. Regular waist, low crotch, button fly and tapered legs.
Canvas hi-tops with a hook and loop fastening and lacing at the front, and a loop at the back. Mesh linings and insoles and rubber soles.
Long coat in soft pile with notch lapels, concealed press-studs down the front, long raglan sleeves and concealed pockets in the side seams. Lined.
Short dress in a patterned crêpe weave with buttons down the front, a seam at the waist and 3/4-length sleeves. Unlined.
Large shopper in imitation leather with two handles and a concealed magnetic fastener at the top. One zipped inner compartment. Size 13x40x40 cm.
Boxer shorts in a cotton weave with an elasticated waist, long legs and button fly.
Long-sleeved jumper in a soft, fluffy knit with slits in the sides. Slightly longer at the back.

Lightweight down jacket in a quilted weave with a ribbed stand-up collar, zip down the front and welt side pockets with a concealed zip. Filling 70% recycled down and 30% recycled feathers from Re:Down®.
Trousers in stretch twill made from a cotton blend. Skinny fit with an adjustable, elasticated waist, zip fly and button, fake front pockets, real back pockets, flap leg pockets and narrow hems.

Calf-length dress in satin with a round neckline, an opening with a button at the back of the neck, and a concealed zip at the back. Short, wide sleeves that finish at the elbow, a seam at the waist and a gently flared, softly draping skirt. Lined at the top.
LOVE STORIES x H&M. Sleeveless satin nightslip with a lace trim at the top, V-neck, narrow, adjustable shoulder straps, and a straight-cut hem with slits in the sides.
Trousers in twill with a high, elasticated paper bag waist and detachable belt with a plastic buckle. Pockets in the side seams and tapered legs.
Socks in a soft, fine-knit cotton blend with elasticated tops.
Lined balconette bikini top with underwired, padded cups that lift and shape the bust. Silicone trim at the hem, detachable, adjustable shoulder straps, side support and a metal fastener at the back.
Skinny-fit, ankle-length trousers in washed stretch twill with hard-worn details. Adjustable elasticated waist, zip fly and press-stud, fake front pockets, real back pockets and raw-edge hems.
Knee-length chino shorts in stretch cotton twill with an adjustable, elasticated waist, zip fly and button, side pockets and fake back pockets with a button. Detachable elastic braces.
Round-necked T-shirt in soft jersey made from a cotton and modal blend. Slim fit.
Short, fitted dress in cotton jersey with a V-neck and short sleeves.
Vest top in soft jersey with a crocheted lace racer back and gently rounded hem. Slightly longer at the back.
NATHALIE LÉTÉ x H&M. Shorts in an airy, patterned viscose weave with covered elastication and a decorative, tasselled drawstring at the waist. Side pockets and small frill trims at the hems.
T-shirt in soft cotton jersey with a reversible sequin motif on the front and ribbing around the neckline.
Fine-knit gloves in a wool blend with imitation leather trims.
Hat in soft rib-knit cashmere.
Elasticated satin scrunchie.
V-neck body in textured jersey with narrow, adjustable shoulder straps and concealed press-studs at the crotch.
Lightly padded, calf-length gilet in woven fabric made from recycled polyester. Press-studs down the front, large patch pockets and high slits at the sides.

Coach jacket in a printed weave with a collar, press-studs down the front, side pockets with a press-stud and an inner pocket with a hook and loop fastening. Elasticated cuffs and a drawstring at the hem. Jersey lining.
Longer top in cotton jersey with a decorative tie at the side. Short sleeves and gathers in the sides for a good fit over the tummy.

Hoodie in soft sweatshirt fabric with a kangaroo pocket and jersey-lined hood with a wrapover front. Long, block-coloured sleeves with a seam at the elbows, and ribbing at the cuffs and hem. Soft brushed inside. The cotton content of the hoodie is organic.
T-shirt in soft cotton jersey with a reversible sequin motif on the front and ribbing around the neckline.
Shirt in a cotton weave with a collar, buttons down the front and chest pocket. Yoke at the back, short sleeves with sewn-in turn-ups, and a rounded hem.

Shirt in an airy linen and cotton weave with a turn-down collar, classic front and yoke at the back. Open chest pocket, long sleeves with adjustable buttoning at the cuffs, and a rounded hem. Regular Fit – a classic fit with good room for movement and a gently tapered waist to create a comfortable, tailored silhouette.
Short-sleeved sports top in fast-drying functional fabric with a print motif and reflective details.
Long-sleeved top in soft cotton jersey with a round neck. Slightly longer at the back.
Calf-length skirt in a rib knit containing glittery threads with an elasticated waist. Short jersey lining skirt.
Low-necked T-shirt in soft slub jersey made from a cotton and modal blend with a seam down the back.

Padded parka in woven fabric with a lined, drawstring hood and zip down the front. Sleeve pocket and side pockets with a flap and hook and loop fastening, visible, gathered seams down the back and sleeves, and a drawstring at the hem. Lined.

5-pocket, ankle-length jeans in washed, stretch denim with hard-worn details, a high waist, zip fly and button and skinny legs with raw-edge hems. Embrace – denim with a smart stretch function that moulds to the body for a comfortable, flattering silhouette.

Waterproof hi-top trainers in imitation leather with canvas details. Adjustable hook and loop tab at the top, elasticated lacing at the front and a loop front and back. Pile linings and insoles. The hi-tops have a water-repellent coating without fluorocarbons.
Tops in soft organic cotton jersey.
Short shorts in a cotton weave with elastication at the back of the waist, a fake fly and patch front pockets. Wide panel at the waist for optimum comfort.
Derby shoes with open lacing, fabric insoles, and imitation leather and fabric linings. Rubber soles.
Short, straight-cut dress in airy, sequin-embroidered chiffon with a round neck with an opening and concealed button at the back, dropped shoulders and half-length sleeves. Jersey inner dress.
Leggings in heavy, organic cotton jersey with a soft brushed inside. Skinny fit with an easy pull-on, elasticated waist.

Shirt in woven fabric with a cutaway collar, French front and yoke at the back. Long sleeves with buttoned cuffs, and a rounded hem. The shirt is made from COOLMAX® functional fabric, a unique, soft, comfortable and fast-drying polyester fibre that efficiently wicks moisture while regulating temperature.
Baby Exclusive. T-shirts in soft organic cotton jersey with buttons at the top and short sleeves.
Espadrilles with a braided jute trim around the soles, elastic gores in the sides and a loop at the back. Cotton linings and insoles and fluted rubber soles.
Trunks in stretch cotton jersey with flatlock seams, an elasticated waist, lined front and mid-length legs.

Fully lined swimsuit with a V-neck, adjustable shoulder straps and cups with removable inserts that shape the bust and provide good support. Seam and a double layer of fabric under the bust, gathers in the sides for best fit over the tummy, and medium coverage at the back. The polyester content of the swimsuit is recycled.
5-pocket trousers in washed superstretch twill with a regular waist, zip fly with a button and slim legs.
Satin-covered metal Alice band with faux fur pompoms at the top.
Long-sleeved top in soft modal and cotton jersey with a rounded hem and slits in the sides. Slightly longer at the back.
Sleeveless blouse in woven fabric with a V-neck, concealed button placket and rounded hem.

Short tunic in a cotton weave decorated with frill trims that have overlocked edges. Grandad collar, buttons at the top and long sleeves with buttoned cuffs. Frill trim at the back that continues down the sleeves, and a gathered seam at the hem for added volume. Unlined.
Short skirt in stretch cotton twill with pleats at the top, a fake wrapover at the front, side pockets, and a visible zip and tie at the side. Unlined.
Baby Exclusive. Rib-knit hat in soft wool.
Straight-cut, short-sleeved shirt in a cotton and viscose weave with a resort collar, French front and yoke at the back.
Cropped printed T-shirt in cotton jersey with a cut-off, raw-edge hem.
Hipster briefs in jersey made from a cotton blend with lace trims, a low waist, lined gusset, wide sides and cutaway coverage at the back.
Lace swimsuit with lined, triangular cups with removable inserts, an open back and narrow shoulder straps that cross and tie at the back. Lined over the bust and at the bottom.
Short jumper in a loose knit containing some mohair with dropped shoulders, long sleeves and ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem.
Top in soft, printed cotton jersey with short puff sleeves.
ANNA GLOVER x H&M. Short skirt in patterned, textured fabric with a sewn-in wrapover with pleats at the front and a concealed zip and button at the back. Unlined.
Patterned swim shorts with an elasticated drawstring waist and a fake fly. Soft mesh inner shorts.
Long-sleeved top in soft organic cotton jersey with a round, ribbed neckline.
Ribbed, calf-length dress in a soft, fine knit with a V-neck, decorative buttons down the front, long sleeves and slits in the sides.
Short dungaree dress in soft fabric with adjustable straps with metal fasteners at the front. Lined at the top.
Trousers in soft cotton corduroy with concealed elastication and a drawstring at the waist, a fake fly, diagonal front pockets, welt back pockets and straight legs.
Hi-tops in imitation suede with a padded edge, elasticated lacing at the front and a loop at the back. Mesh linings and insoles and rubber soles.
Fine-knit socks in a soft cotton blend with a fold-down shaft and soft terry inside. Sizes 3-9 with anti-slip protectors.

Long-sleeved jumper in a soft knit containing some wool. Zip at the back, dropped shoulders, ribbing around the neckline, cuffs and hem, and slits in the sides. The polyester content of the jumper is recycled.
5-pocket, ankle-length jeans in washed, stretch denim with an extra-high waist, zip fly and button, and slim legs.
Leggings in heavy, organic cotton jersey with glittery details and a soft brushed inside. Skinny fit with an easy pull-on, elasticated waist.
Imitation leather trainers with a hook and loop fastening at the front, fabric linings and insoles and rubber soles.
Wide, high-waisted shorts in woven fabric with a sewn-in tie belt and pleats at the top. Fly with a concealed zip, side pockets and fake welt back pockets.
Long-sleeved dresses in soft organic cotton jersey with a gathered seam at the hips and a gently flared skirt.
Long-sleeved tops in organic cotton with a round neckline and gathers in the sides for best fit over the tummy. One top is ribbed.
Joggers in an airy viscose weave with an elasticated waist with a tasselled drawstring, side pockets and tapered legs with covered elastic at the hems.
Sunglasses with metal and plastic frames and tinted, UV-protective lenses.
